            "notes": "The deck revolves around using Grenzo, Dungeon Warden as the commander to aggressively play goblin creatures and disrupt the opponent's strategy with targeted removal and hand disruption spells. The deck aims to quickly overwhelm the opponent with a swarm of goblin creatures and use Grenzo's ability to put them directly onto the battlefield from the bottom of the library. By utilizing a mix of efficient creatures, disruptive spells, and lands that provide mana fixing, the deck can apply constant pressure and maintain card advantage. The strategy focuses on maintaining a fast-paced tempo, applying pressure early in the game, and utilizing the goblin tribal synergy to dominate the board and secure victory."
