            "notes": "This deck focuses on utilizing the commander, Marath, Will of the Wild, to create a board presence early on and overwhelm the opponent with aggressive creatures. The deck includes cards that synergize with Marath's ability to put +1/+1 counters on creatures, such as Hardened Scales and Conclave Mentor. Additionally, the deck includes cards that can generate mana quickly, like Devoted Druid and Earthcraft, allowing for explosive plays and efficient casting of spells. With a mix of ramp, removal, and powerful creatures, the deck aims to establish a dominant board state and pressure the opponent into making unfavorable trades. The strategy revolves around being proactive and staying ahead on board presence to secure victory."
